snippet.title: DIO - Rainbow In The Dark (Full Band Cover)
snippet.description:
Hey, folks. It’s been forever. Today is my birthday and we prepared this video as my birthday special.

This is DIO - Rainbow In The Dark Cover

It took us a year to get through the many twists and turns and the video was completed. I would like to thank all the great musicians who have worked for this cover.

It's been our intentions to make this cover an individual thing and not a direct copy of the original. It's up to you to decide whether the attempt has been successful or not. Please, visit our channels below and don't forget to like it and subscribe the channel for more videos.

And please leave some comments what you think of this video and stayed tune for the next one. It will be on my channel very soon!

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Lead Vocals, Harmony Vocals, Video Editing
Leo Peña (Jotun Studio, Spain) - Rhythm Guitars, Producing, Mixing and Mastering
HyunSoo Kim (ex Flashback, South Korea) - Lead Guitars
Peter Uvén (Symmetric Chaos, Sweden) - Bass Guitars
Emilio Kanina (Jotun Studio, Spain) - Drums 
Alex Nasla (Symmetric Chaos, USA) - Keyboards
